Enum Class EventType

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<EventType>
cz.cvut.fel.omo.smartfarm.chainOfResponsibility.EventType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<EventType>, Constable
public enum EventType extends Enum<EventType>
Enum defining different types of events that can occur in a smart farm environment. These events are categorized into different sections based on their relevance to equipment, fields, farmers, or animals.
